  "tooltip.neoecoae.computation_system": "The core of the computation subsystem",
  "tooltip.neoecoae.computation_system_desc.0": "The computation subsystem introduces virtual Crafting Processors (vCPUs):",
  "tooltip.neoecoae.computation_system_desc.1": "The host provides only one vCPU to the ME network at a time, with capacity equal to all currently available bytes in the subsystem",
